@startuml add-date
title Add Date User Flow

actor User
participant "Dashboard" as Dashboard
participant "Add Date Modal" as Modal
participant "API" as API
participant "Database" as DB

User -> Dashboard: Click "Add Date" button
Dashboard -> Modal: Open add date modal

Modal -> User: Display form\n(Type, Name, Date, Notes)

User -> Modal: Select date type\n(Birthday/Anniversary)
User -> Modal: Enter person name
User -> Modal: Select date
User -> Modal: Add optional notes
User -> Modal: Click "Save"

Modal -> API: POST /api/dates
API -> DB: Insert new date record
DB --> API: Confirm insert
API --> Modal: Return success

Modal -> User: Show success notification
Modal -> Dashboard: Close modal & refresh list
Dashboard -> User: Display updated date list

@enduml
